  "body": "- [X] I've asked for help in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle) before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nWhen running a Truffle test, I need to send ether via `web3.eth.sendTransaction()`. I am using the global `web3` variable to do this. This forms a tx with nonce 1 higher than it should be. Note that in the same test, I am making a call to `myContract.myMethod()`, which tracks the nonce correctly.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\nHere is my code:\r\n\r\n```\r\nit('Should register serial numbers for 4 test devices', function() {\r\n    Promise.each(serials, function(s, j) {\r\n        registry.register(infura_addrs[j+1], s, { from: deployer })\r\n        .then((success) => {\r\n          return new Promise((resolve, reject) => web3.eth.sendTransaction({ from: deployer, value: 0.1*Math.pow(10, 18), to: infura_addrs[j+1] }, (err, result) => err ? reject(err) : resolve(result)))\r\n        .then(() => { assert.equal(1, 1) })\r\n        .catch((err) => { assert.equal(err, null, err) })\r\n    })\r\n  })\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nThe test to pass.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nAn error is thrown of form:\r\n\r\n```\r\n/Users/alexmiller/meta-gridplus/gridplus/gridx-hub/node_modules/truffle/build/cli.bundled.js:213982\r\n        throw reason;\r\n        ^\r\nAssertionError: ProviderError: Error: the tx doesn't have the correct nonce. account has nonce of: 448 tx has nonce of: 449\r\n    at runCall (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/ethereumjs-testrpc/build/cli.node.js:88086:10)\r\n    at /usr/local/lib/node_modules/ethereumjs-testrpc/build/cli.node.js:11855:24\r\n    at replenish (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/ethereumjs-testrpc/build/cli.node.js:8948:17)\r\n    at iterateeCallback (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/ethereumjs-testrpc/build/cli.node.js:8933:17)\r\n    at /usr/local/lib/node_modules/ethereumjs-testrpc/build/cli.node.js:8908:16\r\n    at /usr/local/lib/node_modules/ethereumjs-testrpc/build/cli.node.js:11860:13\r\n    at /usr/local/lib/node_modules/ethereumjs-testrpc/build/cli.node.js:74400:16\r\n    at replenish (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/ethereumjs-testrpc/build/cli.node.js:74347:25)\r\n    at /usr/local/lib/node_modules/ethereumjs-testrpc/build/cli.node.js:74356:9\r\n    at eachLimit (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/ethereumjs-testrpc/build/cli.node.js:74280:36)\r\n    at /usr/local/lib/node_modules/ethereumjs-testrpc/build/cli.node.js:75460:16\r\n    at VM.AsyncEventEmitter.emit (/usr/local/lib/node_modules/ethereumjs-testrpc/build/cli.node.js:74051:3): expected { Object (message, stack, ...) } to equal null\r\n    at registry.register.then.then.catch (/Users/alexmiller/meta-gridplus/gridplus/gridx-hub/truffle/test/registry.js:95:34)\r\n    at <anonymous>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Sierra 10.12.6 \r\n* Truffle version: 3.4.4\r\n* Ethereum client: INFURA (remote deployment)\r\n* node version: 8.2.1\r\n* npm version: 5.3.0\r\n",
