    "body": "I had a similar issue on deployments (incorrect nonce). I solved my issue by changing my deployment from:\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\nreturn deployer.deploy([\r\n    ContractA,\r\n    ContractB\r\n  ]).then(function() {\r\n    return deployer.deploy(ContractC);\r\n  });\r\n```\r\n\r\nto\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\nreturn deployer.deploy(ContractA).then(function() {\r\n  \treturn deployer.deploy(ContractB).then(function() {\r\n  \t\treturn deployer.deploy(ContractC);\r\n  \t});\r\n  });\r\n```",
